--- decideLogDestination() ---
  ✅ public repo + group chat → chat delivery
  ✅ public repo + supergroup → chat delivery
  ✅ public repo + private chat (DM) → dm delivery (already in DM)
  ✅ private repo → dm delivery
  ✅ internal-visibility repo → dm delivery
  ✅ unknown visibility → dm delivery (fail-closed)
  ✅ isPublic:true but visibility unknown → dm delivery (fail-closed)
  ✅ non-isolation session → reject (issue #1686 R4)
  ✅ isolation:"direct" → reject
  ✅ unknown session → reject
  ✅ sessionInfo.isolationBackend overrides missing status.isolation
  ✅ sessionInfo.isolationBackend + private repo → dm

--- resolveLogPath() ---
  ✅ prefers statusResult.logPath when present
  ✅ falls back to isolation/<backend>/<uuid>.log
  ✅ falls back to direct/<uuid>.log when no backend
  ✅ returns null when uuid is missing and no logPath is provided

